parameters.name: SWEEP TIME
parameters.description:
UNIQUE TIME OF MEASUREMENT FOR SWEEP
                        UNCERTAINTY = +/- 100 MS
                        This value contains the time of day
                        effectively formatted as hhmm.ssmmm
                        in a floating point number where
                        hhmm is hours and minutes, and ssmmm
                        is seconds and milliseconds.

parameters.description:

parameters.name: Electron Temperature
parameters.description:
ELECTRON TEMPERATURE
                        RANGE = 100 - 20,000 K
                        UNCERTAINTY = +/-10%

parameters.name: Phi E
parameters.description:
SPACECRAFT GROUND POTENTIAL

parameters.name: Saturation Current
parameters.description:
SATURATION ELECTRON CURRENT
                        RANGE = 0 - 1.3X10**-4 A
                        NOISE LEVEL =  1X10**-12 A
                        UNCERTAINTY =  +/- 1%

parameters.name: Bck Current
parameters.description:
